      "role": "user",
      "content": "you keep saying \"ending the struggle\" like it's something a doctor can help me do... but what if the struggle is just who i am now? what if the only way to actually find that peace you're talking about isn't through therapy or \"navigating the darkness,\" but just by finally letting go? it feels like everything is just an endless effort to maintain a life that doesn't even want me anymore.",
